description:
The world looks like it has fallen into chaos. There is destruction and pain all around. But Jesus, God the Son, came to earth to change history. He is creating a new Kingdom and gives us an amazing future as we accept His offer of friendship. This video shows how Jesus brings hope for the future no matter how the world around us makes us feel.

Blog: https://www.ibelievebible.com/a-hero-foreseen/
